<p>Today John and Dave are joined by special guest, Michael Johnston, of Applr and We Have Communicators fame! Michael comes on the show to talk about Applr, but also joins the geeks for their whole discussion. In addition to Applr, your two (three?) favorite geeks go through some geek challenges, then it&#39;s on to answering&nbsp;<em>your</em> questions. Don&#39;t miss it!</p>
